728021f-a.title: Queens: Springfield Boulevard - 99th Avenue
728021f-a.text:
Springfield Boulevard, adjoining the N. E. corner of 99th Avenue,
showing an old mansion. This house appears on Wolverton's 1891 map
of Cueens Village, but its ownership is not indicated. It lay directly
south of W. Creed's property.
March 4, 1927
P. L. Sperr
